  ¡§Chit-e5 si7 goa2 e5 eN-a2.¡¨ A-hoa eng7 pou3 cho3 chit8-sian eN-a2 lai5 kap i kong2 oe7. ¡§Ma-ma beh chhoa7 li2 chhut-khi3 thit-tho5, beh che7-chhia khi3 ke-a2, li2 tioh8 kin2-kin2 loah li2 e5 thau5-mng5; li2 e5 thau5-mng5 chin-sui2, ia7 tioh8 oaN7 hit-nia2 ma-ma cho3 hou7 li2 e5 ang5-saN. Li2 chheng7 hit-nia2 chin-chiaN3 sui2, oe5 tioh8 chheng7 hit-siang bo5-toa3 e5, na7 bo5, li2 e5 kha oe7 thiaN3.¡¨ A-hoa chiong iuN2-bu2 siong5 tui3 i kong2 e5 oe7 lai5 tui3 eN-a2 kong2. 
