  Keng-koe3 kui2 geh8-jit8 au7, ti7 chit-e5 ka-teng5 u7 ke-thiN chit8-e5 ta-pou eN-a2. IuN2-bu2 e5 hoaN-hi2 boe7-thang heng5-iong5, in e5 sim-lai7 chiong-jit8 long2 chhiong-moa2 eN-a2 e5 su7, chhin-chhiuN7 tu2-tu2 chiah hoat-hian7 tioh8 seng-oah8 e5 i3-gi7, tu2-tu2 chiah kiN3-tioh8 jit8-kng chit8-iuN7, moa2-moa2 e5 heng7-hok khoai3-lok8. In bo5-me5 bo5-jit8 lai5 chiau3-kou3 chit8-e5 chiang2-tiong e5 po2-poe3. 
  ¡§Chin hok-siong3 e5 bin7, bak8-chiu chin u7 chai5-khi3! Chit-e5 eN-a2 toa7-han3 khi2-lai5 oe7 cho3 gau5 lang5, lan2 tioh8 lai5 boe2 chit8-nia2 siong7-teng2 e5 saN hou7 i chheng7, chit-ho7 peng5-siong5 e5 saN khah bo5 hah8 i, ia7 tioh8 chit8-nia2 chin kui3-khi3 e5 than2-na2, na7 khah toa7-han3 chiu7 thang am than2-na2 chhut-khi3 thit-tho5. Koh bo5 ku2 chiu7 oe7 kiaN5, ia7 oe7 kong2 oe7, oe7 kio3 pa-pa ma-ma, lan2 chiu7 chhoa7 i kau3 iu3-ti7-hng5, i sou2 chheng7 e5 si7 te7-it sui2 e5 saN. Ah, hit-e5 hoaN-hi2, hit-e5 heng7-hok!¡¨ 
