  ¡§Li2 si7 goa2 e5 eN-a2, goa2 e5 po2-poe3, goa2 beh cho3 chit8-nia2 chin sui2 e5 saN hou7 li2 chheng7, si7 peh8-sek e5 saN, na7 bo5, chiah-nih8 koaN5 goa2 e5 eN-a2 oe7 koaN5-tioh8, ouh, goa2 e5 eN-a2 na7 koaN5-tioh8, goa2 beh an2-choaN2,goa2 chiu7 siong-sim, goa2 beh kong2, goa2 e5 siN3-mia7, goa2 e5 khoai3-lok8!¡¨ A-hoa chiong iuN2-bu2 e5 oe7 lai5 teng5-sut8 ti7 i e5 ang-a2. Kau3 A-long5 beh tng2-lai5 e5 si5-khek, A-hoa chiu7 pang3-sak i e5 ang-a2 lai5 ti7 thang-a2 piN tan2-hau7 i, ai3 beh thiaN in e5 oe7. 
